Introduction

Element is a fictional girl group featured in the Korean drama Who Is She. The group consists of aspiring idols under UNIS Entertainment, striving to make their debut in the competitive K-pop industry. The members include Oh Doo Ri (played by Jung Ji So), a mysterious and talented trainee with a hidden past; Choi Ha Na (played by Chae Won Bin), an ambitious and hardworking performer; Olla (played by Yue from Lapillus), a charismatic member with a strong stage presence; and Jay (played by Seowon from Lapillus), a skilled dancer and vocalist.

Throughout the drama, Who Is She follows Element’s journey as they train, overcome challenges, and pursue their dreams of becoming successful idols. Their story highlights the struggles and passion behind the glamorous world of K-pop.
